    "description": "SecureD is a hardware based encryption device that offers optimal, fully integrated, protection for stored data in IDE data bus based computer systems. SecureD operates fully transparent at the speed of ATA-6 AT API. SecureD is using AES 128/192/256 bits encryption/decryption, and is 100% operating system independent. No SW is installed. Ideal for encryption of disks in Desktop environment, Laptop, and USB/Firewire connected disks.",
